description: The battle between COBRA and G.I. JOE heats up, as their former comrade, DARK SNAKE EYES, is unleashed on G.I. JOE. With STORM SHADOW on their side, though, the Joes may still be able to turn the tables on COBRA.

volume.name: G.I. Joe: A Real American Hero

description:
The Fantastic four face off against a sentient computer being, insects from another dimension, Johnny trying to get money out of FF and a wawe of molecular instability! We also find out why Reed decided to brand Fantastic four as...well, Fantastic four.

As a bonus, there`s also a story written by Karl Kesel (illustrated by Stuart Immonen and Scott Koblish), in what Thing/Ben Grimm gets really angry.

Collects Fantastic four (vol. 2) 56 and 60-66.
